<subSubSection id="D9F16554FFB4BA18B6FFFCDAB6EBF2F1" pageId="8" pageNumber="627" type="discussion">
Specimens of 
<taxonomicName id="56EB4D5CFFB4BA18B7D5FCDAB640F415" authorityName="J. A. Allen" authorityYear="1906" box="[967,1126,3002,3035]" class="Mammalia" family="Molossidae" genus="Molossus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="627" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="sinaloae">M. sinaloae</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingRegion id="532FF83DFFB4BA18B0DEFCDAB71CF415" box="[1228,1338,3002,3035]" country="Mexico" name="Yucatan" pageId="8" pageNumber="627">Yucatan</collectingRegion>
were described as 
<taxonomicName id="56EB4D5CFFB4BA18B7F4FC82B652F3CD" authorityName="Gonzalez-Ruiz, Ramirez-Pulido &amp; Arroyo-Cabrales" authorityYear="2011" box="[998,1140,3042,3075]" class="Mammalia" family="Molossidae" genus="Molossus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="627" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="alvarezi">M. alvarezi</taxonomicName>
based on morphology. Based on genetic data, individuals of 
<taxonomicName id="56EB4D5CFFB4BA18B756FB50B1FDF39F" authorityName="J. A. Allen" authorityYear="1906" box="[836,987,3120,3153]" class="Mammalia" family="Molossidae" genus="Molossus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="627" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="sinaloae">M. sinaloae</taxonomicName>
from Central and South America cluster with M. alvarexi and not with individuals from Pacific slope of 
<collectingCountry id="E9FC764FFFB4BA18B0EAFBE0B130F306" name="Mexico" pageId="8" pageNumber="627">Mexico</collectingCountry>
where the type locality of 
<taxonomicName id="56EB4D5CFFB4BA18B099FBC7B707F306" authorityName="J. A. Allen" authorityYear="1906" box="[1163,1313,3239,3272]" class="Mammalia" family="Molossidae" genus="Molossus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="627" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="sinaloae">M. sinaloae</taxonomicName>
is located. Therefore, distribution of 
<taxonomicName id="56EB4D5CFFB4BA18B0C1FBAFB13EF2D9" authorityName="Gonzalez-Ruiz, Ramirez-Pulido &amp; Arroyo-Cabrales" authorityYear="2011" class="Mammalia" family="Molossidae" genus="Molossus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="627" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="alvarezi">M. alvarezi</taxonomicName>
was expanded to South America, and distribution of 
<taxonomicName id="56EB4D5CFFB4BA18B549FA7EB3D6F2F1" authorityName="J. A. Allen" authorityYear="1906" box="[347,496,3358,3391]" class="Mammalia" family="Molossidae" genus="Molossus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="627" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="sinaloae">M. sinaloae</taxonomicName>
was restricted to western part of 
<collectingCountry id="E9FC764FFFB4BA18B7A8FA7EB604F2F1" box="[954,1058,3358,3391]" name="Mexico" pageId="8" pageNumber="627">Mexico</collectingCountry>
. Monotypic.
</subSubSection>
</paragraph>
